trans-unit.source: Compiler Warnings C4000 Through C4199 | Microsoft Docs
The articles in this part of the documentation contain information about a subset of the Visual C++ compiler warnings.
You can access the information here or, in the **Output** window in Visual Studio, you can select a warning number and then choose the F1 key.
Please choose the Technical Support command on the Visual C++
Help menu, or open the Technical Support help file for more information
